metadata.name: Non-Fungible Fitness Pass
metadata.description:
The Non-Fungible Fitness pass is a fitness membership pass that will grant you access to online fitness classes, discounted online personal training sessions, self-paced workout programs and other health & fitness resources.

Token-gated access valid December 15th, 2022 through December 31st, 2023. 

Join the Non-Fungible Fitness discord to verify your token or visit our token-gated community page at https://www.mintgate.io

Our mission is to build an interactive wellness-focused community, while providing resources and tools to help motivate you on your journey to better health.

Founded by certified fitness and health professional Kalla @kallamindbody
